1.00	Pussy_Pop	40 Dayz &amp; 40 Nightz	40 Dayz &amp; 40 Nightz is rapper Xzibit's second album, which was released on August 25, 1998. It is often considered Xzibit's greatest album. The album featured four singles "What U See Is What U Get", "3 Card Molly", "Los Angeles Times" and "Pussy Pop". "What U See Is What U Get" in particular not only earned Xzibit's highest charting in his career but has also been hailed by some as one of the greatest rap songs of all time.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c0/40_Dayz_%26_40_Nightz.JPG/220px-40_Dayz_%26_40_Nightz.JPG
